# Data and Airtime VTU Application

## Overview
This project is a full-stack application that allows users to:
- Register and log in.
- Fund a wallet.
- Purchase mobile data and airtime.
- View transaction history.

## Tech Stack
- Frontend: React.js
- Backend: Node.js with Express.js
- Database: MongoDB
- Authentication: JWT
- Payment Gateway: Paystack
- VTU API: VTpass or Reloadly
